\subtree[stt-00RB]{
\title{Necklaces}
\taxon{Definition}
\author{fredrikbakke}
\date{2025-05-21}

\p{
A \em{necklace} is a finite [wedge](Core.BipointedWedgeSums) of
[standard simplices](stt-00E1) glued end to end

##{
\Delta^{n_1} \vee \cdots \vee \Delta^{n_k}.
}
}

\agda{
Necklace-length : List ‚Ąē ‚Üí ‚Ąē
Necklace-length = foldr _+‚Ąē_ 0
{-# NOINLINE Necklace-length #-}

Necklace‚ąó‚ąó : List ‚Ąē ‚Üí Type‚ąó‚ąó ūĚďė
Necklace‚ąó‚ąó [] = őĒ‚ąó‚ąó 0
Necklace‚ąó‚ąó (m ‚ą∑ N) = Wedge‚ąó‚ąó (őĒ‚ąó‚ąó m) (Necklace‚ąó‚ąó N)

Necklace : List ‚Ąē ‚Üí Type ūĚďė
Necklace N = Type‚ąó‚ąó.Carrier (Necklace‚ąó‚ąó N)

Necklace-is-0-truncated
  : (N : List ‚Ąē) ‚Üí is-truncated 0 (Necklace N)
Necklace-is-0-truncated []
  = őĒ-is-0-truncated
Necklace-is-0-truncated (m ‚ą∑ N)
  = Wedge-is-0-truncated őĒ-is-0-truncated (Necklace-is-0-truncated N)

Necklace-is-set
  : (N : List ‚Ąē) ‚Üí is-set (Necklace N)
Necklace-is-set N
  = is-set‚Üźis-truncated (Necklace-is-0-truncated N)
}
}


\subtree[stt-00RS]{
\title{The simplex inclusion of a binary wedge of simplices}
\taxon{Definition}
\author{fredrikbakke}
\date{2025-05-21}


\agda{
Wedge-őĒ-incl
  : (m n : ‚Ąē)
  ‚Üí Type‚ąó‚ąó.Carrier (Wedge‚ąó‚ąó (őĒ‚ąó‚ąó m) (őĒ‚ąó‚ąó n))
  ‚Üí őĒ^ (m +‚Ąē n)
Wedge-őĒ-incl m n = cogap
  (mk-cocone (őĒ-pad-0 n) (őĒ-prepend-1 m) (őĽ _ ‚Üí őĒ-ext (compute-őĒ-pad-0-őĒ-1 n)))

Wedge-őĒ-incl‚ąó‚ąó
  : (m n : ‚Ąē)
  ‚Üí map‚ąó‚ąó (Wedge‚ąó‚ąó (őĒ‚ąó‚ąó m) (őĒ‚ąó‚ąó n)) (őĒ‚ąó‚ąó (m +‚Ąē n))
Wedge-őĒ-incl‚ąó‚ąó m n .map‚ąó‚ąó.hom = Wedge-őĒ-incl m n
Wedge-őĒ-incl‚ąó‚ąó m n .map‚ąó‚ąó.pres-src = őĒ-ext (compute-őĒ-pad-0-őĒ-0 n)
Wedge-őĒ-incl‚ąó‚ąó m n .map‚ąó‚ąó.pres-tgt = őĒ-ext (compute-őĒ-prepend-1-őĒ-1 m)
}
}


\subtree[stt-00RD]{
\title{The simplex inclusion of a necklace}
\taxon{Definition}
\author{fredrikbakke}
\date{2026-05-21}

\p{
Every #{n}-necklace has a canonical bipointed inclusion into the #{n}-simplex.
}

\agda{
Necklace-incl‚ąó‚ąó
  : (N : List ‚Ąē)
  ‚Üí map‚ąó‚ąó (Necklace‚ąó‚ąó N) (őĒ‚ąó‚ąó (Necklace-length N))
Necklace-incl‚ąó‚ąó [] = id‚ąó‚ąó (őĒ‚ąó‚ąó 0)
Necklace-incl‚ąó‚ąó (m ‚ą∑ N) = map‚ąó‚ąó-‚ąė
  (Wedge-őĒ-incl‚ąó‚ąó m (Necklace-length N))
  (Wedge-map‚ąó‚ąó (id‚ąó‚ąó (őĒ‚ąó‚ąó m)) (Necklace-incl‚ąó‚ąó N))

Necklace-incl : (N : List ‚Ąē) ‚Üí Necklace N ‚Üí őĒ^ (Necklace-length N)
Necklace-incl N = map‚ąó‚ąó.hom (Necklace-incl‚ąó‚ąó N)
}
}
